---
---

<div class="insight-wrapper">
  <div class="insight-diagram">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 900 320" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="diagram-svg">
      <!-- ANTES: bloque izquierdo -->
      <rect x="40" y="40" width="280" height="240" rx="12" fill="none" stroke="#222" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="180" y="30" text-anchor="middle" class="label-small">Antes</text>

      <!-- Notificaciones mezcladas -->
      <!-- Críticas (púrpura) -->
      <rect x="60" y="60" width="240" height="32" rx="6" fill="#ede8ff" stroke="#7611a6" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="180" y="81" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item critical">⚠ Orden de compra pendiente</text>

      <rect x="60" y="100" width="240" height="32" rx="6" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#ccc" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="180" y="121" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item">Actualización del sistema</text>

      <rect x="60" y="140" width="240" height="32" rx="6" fill="#ede8ff" stroke="#7611a6" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="180" y="161" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item critical">⚠ Licitación cierra hoy</text>

      <rect x="60" y="180" width="240" height="32" rx="6" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#ccc" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="180" y="201" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item">Nuevo documento publicado</text>

      <rect x="60" y="220" width="240" height="32" rx="6" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#ccc" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="180" y="241" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item">Recordatorio de acreditación</text>

      <text x="180" y="272" text-anchor="middle" class="label-overflow">+ 95 notificaciones más...</text>

      <!-- FLECHA central -->
      <line x1="340" y1="160" x2="420" y2="160" stroke="#222" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <polygon points="420,155 432,160 420,165" fill="#222"/>
      <text x="386" y="150" text-anchor="middle" class="label-insight">Data +</text>
      <text x="386" y="167" text-anchor="middle" class="label-insight">Insights</text>

      <!-- DESPUÉS: dos bloques derechos -->
      <!-- Sección crítica -->
      <rect x="450" y="40" width="200" height="115" rx="12" fill="none" stroke="#7611a6" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="550" y="30" text-anchor="middle" class="label-small critical">Acciones pendientes</text>
      <rect x="468" y="58" width="164" height="28" rx="5" fill="#ede8ff" stroke="#7611a6" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="550" y="77" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item critical">⚠ Orden de compra</text>
      <rect x="468" y="94" width="164" height="28" rx="5" fill="#ede8ff" stroke="#7611a6" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="550" y="113" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item critical">⚠ Licitación cierra hoy</text>
      <rect x="468" y="130" width="164" height="14" rx="5" fill="#f3eeff" stroke="#c9a0f0" stroke-width="0.8"/>

      <!-- Sección informativa -->
      <rect x="450" y="175" width="200" height="105" rx="12" fill="none" stroke="#ccc" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <text x="550" y="165" text-anchor="middle" class="label-small">Notificaciones</text>
      <rect x="468" y="190" width="164" height="24" rx="5" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#ddd" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="550" y="207" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item">Actualización del sistema</text>
      <rect x="468" y="222" width="164" height="24" rx="5" fill="#f5f5f5" stroke="#ddd" stroke-width="1"/>
      <text x="550" y="239" text-anchor="middle" class="label-item">Nuevo documento</text>
      <rect x="468" y="254" width="164" height="14" rx="5" fill="#fafafa" stroke="#eee" stroke-width="0.8"/>

      <!-- Línea de separación derecha -->
      <line x1="680" y1="100" x2="730" y2="100" stroke="#7611a6" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>
      <text x="735" y="97" class="label-tag critical">crítico</text>
      <line x1="680" y1="228" x2="730" y2="228" stroke="#ccc" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 3"/>
      <text x="735" y="225" class="label-tag">informativo</text>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="insight-text">
    <p class="insight-caption">
      Al revisar la data, detectamos que empresas grandes podían recibir hasta <strong>100 notificaciones diarias</strong>. Sin distinción de criticidad, acciones urgentes —como órdenes de compra pendientes o licitaciones por cerrar— se perdían entre avisos informativos. La solución fue dividir la sección en dos: <strong>Acciones pendientes</strong>, con lo que requiere respuesta inmediata, y <strong>Notificaciones</strong>, con el resto del flujo informativo.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .insight-wrapper {
    margin-block: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .diagram-svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    font-family: 'Crimson Pro', Georgia, serif;
  }

  .label-small {
    font-size: 13px;
    fill: #555;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .label-item {
    font-size: 11px;
    fill: #444;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  .label-item.critical {
    fill: #7611a6;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .label-overflow {
    font-size: 10px;
    fill: #aaa;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .label-insight {
    font-size: 11px;
    fill: #888;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .label-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    fill: #aaa;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  .label-tag.critical {
    fill: #7611a6;
  }

  .insight-caption {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 70ch;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .insight-caption strong {
    color: #0a0a14;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
